  • Supported Apps: Netflix|Prime Video|Disney+Hotstar|Youtube
  • Operating System: Android (Google Assistant & Chromecast in-built)
  • Resolution: HD Ready 1366 x 768 Pixels
  • Sound Output: 20 W
  • Refresh Rate: 60 Hz

You can enjoy your favourite movies, catch up on news, and binge-watch TV series on the Xiaomi L32M7-5AIN HD Smart TV. It features an elegant metal frame with a bezel-less design, allowing you to enjoy a widescreen view. In addition, this TV is sure to enhance your aural experience with Dolby Audio, which provides 20 W high-fidelity sound. Furthermore, boasting a HD display and wide colour gamut, this TV provides high-quality visuals.
